tags: Doctor friendliness,Explanation of the health issue,
review: Doctor is very good attitude, and behaviour is friendliness, his smiles give the relief. I, 27 years Male, have visited for lower back pain and suggested for vitamin pills after some test. Still taking the vitamin. I would request Sir, due to seeing current scenario I returned to my native which is small area, and you suggested the pills is not available here which is about to finish. Could you please help to know me alternative of Celol Max. I would be very thankful to you.Regards,Sudama Dutta, fb- sumant Dutta
